      "description": "This meticulously maintained luxury sedan offers a refined driving experience and a professional appearance. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the premium leather seats are in great shape, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All power features, the touchscreen interface, and the premium audio system are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts seamlessly. I have kept a detailed log of all scheduled maintenance, including a recent fluid service and brake inspection. The tires offer plenty of life for the seasons ahead. This is a dependable, well-cared-for vehicle that delivers excellent value for a discerning buyer.",
